<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 09:47:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>跳跃 DNA 序列驱动早期肿瘤生长</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/jumping-dna-sequences-drive-early-tumor-growth</link><description>新的研究表明，LINE-1 逆转录转座子不仅会推动基因，还会在癌症发展的早期引发大规模的结构剧变。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/jumping-dna-sequences-drive-early-tumor-growth.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 09:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/jumping-dna-sequences-drive-early-tumor-growth</guid></item><item><title>两种 δ-连环蛋白（plakophilin 4 和 p120）促进不同类型粘附连接的形成</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/two-%ce%b4-catenins-plakophilin-4-and-p120-promote-formation-of-distinct-types-of-adherens-junctions</link><description>Indrajyoti Indra、Sergey M. Troyanovsky 等人。 （西北大学 Feinberg 医学院）表明，两种 δ-连环蛋白，p120 和 plakophilin-4，分别促进不同的钙粘蛋白聚类模式（α-连环蛋白依赖性和 α-连环蛋白独立性），从而产生不同类型的粘附连接。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/two-ceb4-catenins-plakophilin-4-and-p120-promote-formation-of-distinct-types-of-adherens-junctions.gif" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 09:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/two-%ce%b4-catenins-plakophilin-4-and-p120-promote-formation-of-distinct-types-of-adherens-junctions</guid></item><item><title>生物学，而不是物理学，掌握着现实的关键</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/biology-not-physics-holds-the-key-to-reality</link><description>牛顿通过固定定律和确定性方程描述宇宙三个世纪后，科学可能正在进入一个全新的阶段。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/biology-not-physics-holds-the-key-to-reality.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 09:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/biology-not-physics-holds-the-key-to-reality</guid></item><item><title>这种化合物可以增强小鼠的长期记忆——但仅限于雌性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/this-compound-enhances-long-term-memory-of-mice-but-only-in-females</link><description>醋酸盐有助于雌性啮齿动物形成记忆，但对雄性啮齿动物效果较差。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/this-compound-enhances-long-term-memory-of-mice-but-only-in-females.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 09:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/this-compound-enhances-long-term-memory-of-mice-but-only-in-females</guid></item><item><title>妇科盆腔MRI参考手册</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/reference-handbook-of-gynecologic-pelvic-mri</link><description>妇科盆腔 MRI 的准确解读取决于量身定制的方案、全面的解剖知识和基于病变的系统方法。本综述概述了按病变起源和组织成分进行的分类。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/reference-handbook-of-gynecologic-pelvic-mri2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 08:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/reference-handbook-of-gynecologic-pelvic-mri</guid></item><item><title>抑制 HIV 复制可以预防严重 M 病毒吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/does-suppression-of-hiv-replication-protect-against-severe-m</link><description>结核&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/does-suppression-of-hiv-replication-protect-against-severe-m.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 08:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/does-suppression-of-hiv-replication-protect-against-severe-m</guid></item><item><title>PDE5A+癌症相关成纤维细胞增强胃癌的免疫抑制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/pde5a-cancer-associated-fibroblasts-enhance-immune-suppression-in-gastric-cancer</link><description>GUTImage 来自 Wang 等人题为“GUT”的论文。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pde5a-cancer-associated-fibroblasts-enhance-immune-suppression-in-gastric-cancer.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 08:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/pde5